/wilted.title: Dried Sunflower
/wilted.content:
Dried flowers last **an average of one year** and when the dried flowers are dyed, they even last a couple of years. In compression: fresh flowers only last up to 10 days. So, with dried flowers you are able to create a long-lasting arrangement and bouquet.
